
# 🌐 HTML-CSS-SIZAR

A responsive web design project built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**.  
The main goal of this project is to sharpen my **UI/UX** skills and explore creative front-end development techniques.

---

## 🔧 Features
- ✅ Responsive layout for all devices
- 🎨 Clean and modern interface
- 🧭 Smooth navigation and transitions
- 📁 Well-structured files and organized code

---

## 🧠 What I Learned
- Flexbox & responsive grid design
- UI consistency & design logic
- JavaScript DOM basics
- Creative layout styling and positioning

